Patterns Analysis

Current Patterns

Kappa-leaning streaming architecture with analytical fork
Event-driven ingestion via message bus (Kinesis)
Time-partitioned columnar storage (Parquet) for historical queries
Geospatial indexing via H3
Recommended

Hot/cold storage tiering (Redis hot, Delta Lake cold)
Lambda architecture for explicit batch heatmap + streaming availability split
Hierarchical geospatial aggregation (spot → lot → zone → city) via H3 parent indices
Materialized view pattern in Redshift for heatmap queries
Anti-patterns

Serving navigation apps directly from Redshift (high latency, wrong tool for point lookups)
Treating offline sensors as 'occupied' or 'available' without stale detection
Running batch jobs without orchestration (manual/cron-based brittleness)
